text: Ogonna Franca Chukwudi (born 14 September 1988) is a Nigerian football midfielder. She played for the Italian Lazio club. She also played in the Nigeria women's national team. ==Club career== Chukwudi played for the Umeå IK club in Damallsvenskan.2011 squad in Umeå's website ==International career== Chukwudi was in the 2011 FIFA Women's World Cup.
